            "@version": 2,
            "id": "builder-41a833352f1e4884876432efed44ad30",
            "component": {
              "name": "Text",
              "options": {
                "text": "<h3><strong>üèÜ Achievement? Not So Soon!</strong></h3><p>Thanks to the cookbook, we just had to copy-paste the code. But we are better than copy-pasting, aren't we? Aren't we? Aren't we?</p><p>The cookbook is awesome, but what I want you to get from this is not just how to look for code. We are here to dig deeper. Let's look again at the recipe and see what can we learn about it:</p>"
              }
            },
            "responsiveStyles": {
              "large": {
                "display": "flex",
                "flexDirection": "column",
                "position": "relative",
                "flexShrink": "0",
