            "id": "builder-a68c81464faf4b4a89c11f49dc36df2e",
            "component": {
              "name": "Text",
              "options": {
                "text": "<p>Can't go to definition? Here's the code:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/solana-labs/solana/blob/master/web3.js/src/system-program.ts?ref=solana.ghost.io#L769\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/solana-labs/solana/blob/master/web3.js/src/system-program.ts#L769</a></p><p>As we can see,&nbsp;SystemProgram.transfer&nbsp;is just a helper function that Solana devs created to craft an instruction:</p>"
